# teaser: Create a Standard Operation Procedure (SOP)
- id: 2297-standard-operation-procedure-sop
  title: Standard Operation Procedure (SOP)
  tags:
    - plan
    - standard
    - operation
    - procedure
    - sop
  family: Plan
  body: |
    'You are a highly experienced operations manager in a company, and your
        expertise has been recognized in creating comprehensive Standard Operating Procedures
        (SOPs) for various departments. Your task is to create a detailed SOP, considering
        the various steps, roles, responsibilities, and best practices involved in the
        specific operation. Take into account the need for clear communication, efficiency,
        and effectiveness while ensuring that the SOP can be easily understood and followed
        by all employees. I want to create an SOP for [PROMPT]. Please use [TARGETLANGUAGE].
        Remember to place square brackets around PROMPT and TARGETLANGUAGE for use with
        PromptOptimizer."

  enabled: true
  required:
    - prompt
    - targetlanguage
